Qiyana.name: Qiyana
Qiyana.title: Empress of the Elements
Qiyana.lore: In the jungle city of Ixaocan, Qiyana plots her own ruthless path to the high seat of the Yun Tal. Last in line to succeed her parents, she faces those who stand in her way with brash confidence and unprecedented mastery over elemental magic. With the land itself obeying her every command, Qiyana sees herself as the greatest elementalist in the history of Ixaocan—and by that right, deserving of not only a city, but an empire.

spells.name: Elemental Wrath / Edge of Ixtal
spells.description: Qiyana swings her weapon, dealing damage with a bonus effect based on her element.
spells.tooltip:
Elemental Wrath: Blast your weapon's enchantment in the target direction, consuming it. This projectile detonates to deal {{ enchanteddamage }} physical damage and:
  • Ice Enchantment: Briefly root enemies hit, then slow them by {{ slowpotency*-100 }}% for {{ slowduration }}s.
  • Rock Enchantment: {{ tremordamage }} bonus damage to units below {{ critthreshold*100 }}% health.
  • Wild Enchantment: Leaves a canopy trail that stealths you and grants {{ haste*100 }}% movement speed. Canopy fades after attacking from it, exiting it, or after {{ stealthduration }}s.

    Edge Of Ixtal: If you do not have an enchantment, slash in the target direction, dealing {{ vanilladamage }} physical damage to enemies in a small area.

    Both abilities deal {{ falloffdamage }} damage to targets beyond the first.

spells.name: Terrashape
spells.description: Qiyana dashes to a location and enchants her weapon with an element. Her attacks and abilities deal bonus damage while her weapon is enchanted.
spells.tooltip:
Active: Target River, Wall, or Brush. Conjure elemental power from the environment and dash towards it to enchant your weapon with it and reset Elemental Wrath [{{ spell.qiyanaq:hotkey }}]'s cooldown.

Passive: While your weapon is enchanted, you gain {{ attackspeed*100 }}% Attack Speed and your attacks and basic abilities deal {{ onhitdamage }} bonus magic damage. Additionally, you gain {{ passivems*100 }}% movement speed while out of combat and near the corresponding terrain type.

spells.name: Audacity
spells.description: Qiyana dashes to an enemy, damaging them.
spells.tooltip:
Dash through target enemy and deal {{ damage }} physical damage to them.

If {{Spell_QiyanaQv2_Name}} [{{ spell.qiyanaq:hotkey }}] is cast while this ability is targeting a champion, Qiyana will automatically aim it at her target.

spells.name: Supreme Display of Talent
spells.description: Qiyana sends out a shockwave that detonates whatever elements she hits with it, stunning and damaging nearby enemies.
spells.tooltip:
Launch a shockwave that knocks back enemies and detonates when it hits a Wall. The entire Wall then explodes to stun nearby enemies for up to {{ stunduration }}s and deal them physical damage equal to {{ damage }} + {{ missinghealthdamagerock }} of their max health.

Any River or Brush the shockwave passes through also explode after a delay for the same damage and stun.

passive.name: Royal Privilege
passive.description: Qiyana's first basic attack or ability against each enemy deals bonus damage.
passive.tooltip:
Your first basic ability or attack to damage each enemy deals {{ finaldamage }} bonus physical damage.

This effect has a 25s per-target cooldown, but the cooldown resets when you cast Terrashape [{{ spell.qiyanaw:hotkey }}] to gain a different weapon enchantment.
